<concept id="class_attribute">
  <title>Attributes</title>

  <prolog>
    <author type="creator">Claude Vedovini</author>

    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>class</indexterm>
        <indexterm>attribute</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>

  <conbody>
    <p>An attribute is a named value that represents an intrinsic
    property of a class.</p>

    <p>An attribute does not exist outside of the scope of the instance of the
    class it belongs to.</p>
  </conbody>

